---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About SaaSScout"
	description="Who we are and why we built SaaSScout"
	pubDate={new Date('2026-05-13')}
>
	<p>
		SaaSScout helps freelancers, content creators, and small business owners
		find the right software tools without wading through sponsored listicles
		and fake reviews.
	</p>

	<p>
		Every tool we review, we test. Every comparison is based on real usage,
		not feature-page copy-paste. When a tool has problems, we say so.
	</p>

	<h2>How we make money</h2>
	<p>
		Some links on this site are affiliate links. That means if you sign up
		for a tool through our link, we earn a small commission at no extra cost
		to you. This is how we keep the site running without ads or paywalls.
	</p>
	<p>
		Affiliate relationships never influence our ratings or recommendations.
		We recommend tools we'd use ourselves, and we say no to tools that
		don't meet our standards, regardless of commission.
	</p>
</Layout>
